  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1077">
<l>īrṅkai vitirār kayavar koṭiṟuṭaikkuṅ</l>
<l>kūṉkaiya rallā tavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mean will not (even) shake off (what sticks to) their hands (soon after a meal) to any but those who would break their jaws with their clenched fists.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
